title: Reduce Cake emission per block
body: The current emission for cake is 40 tokens per block, we are seeing how the marketcap is increasing but price remains not so high, whereas CAKE marketcap is ATH, burning seems to not be affecting enormously so a cut in the emission is neccesary although this will imply a reducction in the rewards of  most liquidity pools and staking farm. What would you think will be the most beneficiuous move for CAKE?
